---
import { waLink } from "@/lib/brand"
---

<section id="cta-final" class="relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-950 py-24 lg:py-32">
  <!-- Decorativo: blobs azul Kora no fundo escuro -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-[36rem] h-[36rem] bg-primary-600 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-20"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-[28rem] h-[28rem] bg-primary-500 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-15"></div>
    <!-- grid sutil -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04]"
      style="background-image: linear-gradient(to right, white 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, white 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 64px 64px;"
    ></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary-300 mb-6">
      Vamos conversar
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight leading-[1.02]">
      Pronto pra parar de<br />
      <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-300 to-primary-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        perder lead?
      </span>
    </h2>

    <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-300 mt-7 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Em 5 minutos no WhatsApp, mostro a Kora rodando com o seu próprio caso.
      Sem demo agendada, sem formulário, sem ficar lá esperando.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-center gap-5">
      <a
        href={waLink("Oi! Quero ver a Kora rodando.")}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-500 text-white font-bold px-9 py-5 rounded-full text-lg transition-all shadow-2xl shadow-primary-600/40 hover:shadow-primary-500/50 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413Z"/>
        </svg>
        Falar no WhatsApp agora
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">
          <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>

      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
        Resposta em minutos no horário comercial · Sem formulário · Sem cartão
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
